<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥١١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/549">إِسْحَاقُ </a>سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4092">عَبْدَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5064">فَاطِمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/622">أَسْمَاءَ </a>قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«ذَبَحْنَا عَلَى عَهْدِ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَرَسًا وَنَحْنُ بِالْمَدِينَةِ فَأَكَلْنَاهُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>